import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz';
import Spinner from './Spinner';

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"spinner"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#spinner"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Spinner`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`진행 중인 사항이 있음을 알리기에 유용한 컴포넌트입니다.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"props"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#props"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Props`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Spinner} />
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"basic-usage"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#basic-usage"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Basic usage`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __code={`<Spinner />`} __scope={{props,Spinner}}>
  <Spinner />
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"custom-example"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#custom-example"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Custom example`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={2} __code={`<Spinner size={100} backgroundColor="red" color="pink" />`} __scope={{props,Spinner}}>
  <Spinner
    size={ 100 }
    backgroundColor="red"
    color="pink"
  />
</Playground></MDXTag>
